Package rocks.xmpp.extensions.data.validate.model

Class Validation

  • java.lang.Object
    • rocks.xmpp.extensions.data.validate.model.Validation
  • public final class Validation
extends Object
    The implementation of the <validate/> element in the http://jabber.org/protocol/xdata-validate namespace, which is used to validate form fields.

    This class is immutable.

    See Also:
    XEP-0122: Data Forms Validation, XML Schema
